reviewText:
I arrived very early.
Thank you very much.

This is a good action flick from france.  IT's got converted 3d for this release but it does make the action seem better and more explosive  This is the second in the series and they were both big hits in Europe. We never got a chance to see them here , which is a shame. NOT all foreign films have to be art films.  (to indie movie houses).  This has a decent price and now I have to catch the first one !
